cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below. If you use or
  discuss the study (the judge-vs-floor configuration-controlled results), cite the
  report via its Zenodo DOI.
type: software
title: "Lithrim"
abstract: >-
  A self-hostable evaluation harness for AI agents with a deterministic, tool-grounded
  verification floor beneath LLM-as-judge councils. Labels are true by construction;
  every grade leaves an immutable, rehydratable audit record.
authors:
